data.meta_description: Happy to inform that SWELECT has been awarded for the below catergories by Softdisk SD's No. 1 Company for having completed largest number of rooftop installations in the country till 31st March, 2021, both in number of installations and wattage SD's No. 1 Hybrid solar PV power solution provider of the year. SD's No. 1 Grid sharing solar PV power solution provider of the year. SD's No. 2 SPCU Manufacturer of the year. SD's No. 5 Solar PV panel manufacturer of the year.
